<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="poem116">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi nāmaḻa</l>
<l>nīla viruṅkaḻi nīlaṅ kūmpu</l>
<l>mālaivan taṉṟu maṉṟa</l>
<l>kālai yaṉṉa kālaimun tuṟuttē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh friend, listen!</l>
<l>So that we cry,</l>
<l>The evening in which the blueness of dark blue lotuses close</l>
<l>Has indeed come, resembling the morning,</l>
<l>The wind being early.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
